#: вҒЁ/home/egon/minu projektid/onair-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/config/configRecording.qmlвҒ©:40
msgid "Radio streams are already compressed вҖ” the bit-exact copy IS the maximum quality. Re-encoding (MP3) or unpacking (WAV) can never add quality; choose them only for device compatibility or editing."
