#: вҒЁ/home/egon/minu projektid/onair-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/config/configRecording.qmlвҒ©:70 вҒЁ/home/egon/minu projektid/onair-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qmlвҒ©:1972 вҒЁ/home/egon/minu projektid/onair-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/FullRepresentation.qmlвҒ©:2063
