msgid "Schedules are managed in the widget itself: open the popup, press the music-note button in the footer to open My Music, then press the stopwatch button next to \"My Music\". Pick a station, start time, duration and repeat (once / daily / weekly) вҖ” the widget records in the background, even while nothing is playing."
msgstr "Las programaciones se gestionan en el propio elemento grГЎfico: abra la ventana emergente, pulse el botГіn de la nota musical del pie para abrir Mi mГәsica y luego el botГіn del cronГіmetro junto a В«Mi mГәsicaВ». Elija emisora, hora de inicio, duraciГіn y repeticiГіn (una vez / a diario / semanal); el elemento grГЎfico graba en segundo plano, incluso sin reproducir nada."

#: вҒЁ/home/egon/minu projektid/onair-plasmoid/package/contents/ui/config/configRecording.qmlвҒ©:82
msgid "Recordings are saved to your music folder and are for personal use only вҖ” do not redistribute them."
